.Dd $Mdocdate: July 15 2022 $
.Dt LUA_SETALLOCF 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm lua_setallocf
.Nd changes the allocator function
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In lua.h
.Ft void
.Fn lua_setallocf "lua_State *L" "lua_Alloc f" "void *ud"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Fn lua_setallocf
changes the allocator function of a given state to
.Fa f
with user data
.Fa ud .
